dct_title_s: 最新徳島市街図 / 和楽路屋.
dct_description_sm: Map shows built-up areas, block numbers, railways, bus routes, planned roads, and buildings of interest, including shrines and temples. Relief shown by contours. Depth by fathoms. North oriented to top left. Tourist and historical information on Tokushima on verso with Tokushima-shi zenzu. Tourist and historical information on Tokushima on verso with 徳島市全図..
dct_publisher_sm: 大阪市西区 : 和楽路屋, 昭和41 [1965]
